{"tid":1539794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[再開po][集氣]推到烏克蘭軍官出黎講兩句","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:31:10.000Z","uid":25105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ddce015f16fadbcd6c3cf484e6310db83ac58cf7","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xwasFoa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwasFoa.jpg&h=9307ee55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢叫 Volodymyr Parasyuk<br />\n係烏克蘭革命入面Maidan Defense既軍官<br />\n呢個係佢既twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/parasyukvolod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fparasyukvolod&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcamaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=1999dbd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/parasyukvolod</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識俄文<br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5fd46c45e74d55627a92c78cc9743412973531d4","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識俄文<br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"57b24e7f4522f31e593ce79f0050bdf6401f1967","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識俄文<br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cf8580b4f5cb5fe9a598ff557080aca7047e9adf","tid":1539794,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5669ad01b9c58b8ec4ddf53225612d3209c28263","tid":1539794,"uid":56194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"推，搵識烏克蘭文嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e70a977af9043df5271a716c2c3190d2508d68","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:26:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識俄文<br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"52d4767e449e6fb315261165b5e7dfc1082cd57d","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識烏克蘭文<br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"328bbfac72fa59d3a3ba851003bb21dfe200c303","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識<span style=\"color: gold;\">烏克蘭文</span><br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f201b094cd6b85bb28adf71b5593aeef686a3096","tid":1539794,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人識<span style=\"color: gold;\">烏克蘭文</span><br />\n叫佢幫手開個po/拍段片<br />\n同港人講唔可以停步?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"11eb6e9703d34968a0b9ef4e20064b1bb05858b6","tid":1539794,"uid":25105